These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, jet-ski, helicopter, bus
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Transport   | snowmobile | jet-ski | bus | helicopter |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
House: colonial, victorian, tower, palace
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the victorian house is on the left of the palace house##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the colonial house##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| House   | tower | colonial  | victorian  | palace |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, lily, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who growslily is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower          | aconite | lily | dahlia    | balloon-flower      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, pall-mall, dunhill, tiparillo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the pall-mall-smoker is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | alhambra | pall-mall | dunhill |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
4 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, dog, pony
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the fan of punk##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Pet   | rat | pony | dog | hedgehog |

