.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, gospel, country, hip-hop
1. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of metal is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | gospel     | metal  | country  |

