.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, malaysian, chinese, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
2. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
4. the nigerian is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the thai is between the nigerian and the malaysian##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the thai and the owner of the goat##2
8. the thai is on the left or right of the malaysian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Nationality   | malaysian | thai      | nigerian | chinese |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

