.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, journalist, engineer, security-guard
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the analyst is between the journalist and the person eating pepper##2
4. the analyst is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Job    | security-guard     | journalist | analyst     | engineer  |

