.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, cooking, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | cooking       | sudoku   | traveling | writing |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

