.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, writing-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is writing-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is writing-polo is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku   | writing   | gardening      | puzzles      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | writing-polo | biathlon |

