.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, carrot, cherry, lemon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, zombie, epic, superhero
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
3. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cherry is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching epic movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | carrot  | cherry  | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | epic | sports | zombie   |

