.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, gospel, hip-hop, metal
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the fan of funk is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of gospel##2
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Music-Genre   | metal | gospel         | funk   | hip-hop |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

