3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
5. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
