.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, gardening, sudoku
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, plum, corn, banana
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person eating plum is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
5. the person eating plum is between the person eating banana and the person eating corn##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | gardening | board-games | chess    |
| Food   | corn | plum  | banana     | raspberry |

