.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Pet     | ferret      | mouse       | goldfish | rat     |

