.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, apple, radish, lime
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person eating apple is in an even position##4
2. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person eating onion and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the person eating apple is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating lime##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Food         | onion | radish   | lime | apple |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 